ivisible]] (National)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/Marie4Congress/status/1195025582171607047|title=I am so honored by the NATIONAL endorsement from @IndivisibleTeam. We will win with the support of grassroots groups like Indivisible and @CCIL3rd that are fighting for better representation in every community. Let's finish what we started in 2018\u2014it's a #NewDayInIL03. #IL03pic.twitter.com/aQfjTmStpm|first=Marie|last=Newman|date=November 14, 2019|accessdate=January 12, 2020}}</ref>\n*[[Indivisible movement|Indivisible]] Brookfield<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Illinois [[National Organization for Women|NOW]]<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Indivisible Chicago<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indivisiblechicago.com/indivisible-chicago-marie-newman-endorsement|title=Indivisible Chicago Marie Newman Endorsement|website=Indivisible Chicago|accessdate=January 12, 2020}}</ref>\n* Indivisible Chicago-South Side<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/IndivChi_South/status/1164555088406470656|title=BREAKING: Indivisible Chicago-South Side is proud to endorse Marie Newman for Congress in #IL03. Support @Marie4Congress for a #NewDayinIL03!pic.twitter.com/H8qJTLI0Ge|first=Indivisible Chicago-South|last=Side|date=August 22, 2019|accessdate=January 12, 2020}}</ref>\n* Indivisible DuPage<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Indivisible IL-09 Andersonville-Edgewater<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Indivisible La Grange/La Grange Park<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Indivisible Loyola\n* Indivisible West Suburban Action League<ref name=\"marienewmanforcongress.com\"/>\n* Jane Addams Seniors in Action<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1257183204465566&id=731569880360237|title=Jane Addams Seniors in Action|website=www.facebook.com}}</ref>\n*[[Justice Democrats]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.justicedemocrats.com/candidates/|title=Justice Democrats &#124; It's #OurTime|website=ju