aforcongress.com/endorsements|title=Endorsements|website=Kina Collins for Congress|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-31}}</ref>\n* Women's March Illinois<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/womensmarchillinois/posts/2842228739225540|title=Meet Women's March - Illinois supported candidate, Kina Collins, and let's help get a new powerhouse representative from Chicago to DC on March 17, 2020!|last=Women's March Illinois|date=January 24, 2020|website=facebook.com|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-01-31}}</ref>\n* Northside Democracy for America<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.northsidedfa.com/|title=Northside Democracy for America|last=|first=|date=|website=Northside Democracy for America|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200104152950/https://www.northsidedfa.com/|archive-date=2020-01-04|access-date=2020-01-31}}</ref>\n* Blue America<ref name=\":0\" />\n* Good Kids Mad City<ref name=\":0\" />\n* Illinois Youth Climate Strike<ref name=\":0\" />\n\n'''Elected officials'''\n* [[Anna Moeller]], [[Illinois House of Representatives|Illinois House]] Representative for the 43rd district<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.austinweeklynews.com/News/Articles/1-30-2020/Austin-congressional-hopeful-nabs-suburban-endorsements-/|title=Austin congressional hopeful nabs suburban endorsements|last=Sheridan|first=Stacey|date=January 30, 2020|website=austinweeklynews.com|language=en-US|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-01-31}}</ref>\n*[[Jeanette Taylor]], alderman for the 20th ward in [[Chicago City Council]]<ref name=\":1\" />\n*Susan Buchanan, [[Oak Park, Illinois|Oak Park]] Village Trustee<ref name=\":1\" />\n*Arti Walker-Peddakotla, Oak Park Village Trustee<ref name=\":1\" />\n*Patty Henek, [[River Forest, Illinois|River Forest]] Village Trustee<ref name=\":1\" />\n*Erika Bachner, River Forest Village Trustee<ref name=\":1\" />\n*Katie Avalos, member of the [[River Forest Public Scho