020\n}}\n{{Election box  candidate with party link no change\n| candidate = [[Darin LaHood]] (incumbent)\n| party = Republican Party (United States)\n| votes = \n| percentage = \n}}\n{{Election box total no change\n| votes = \n| percentage = 100.0\n}}\n{{Election box end}}\n\n==References==\n{{notelist}}\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n;Find your district/elected officials\n* [https://elections.il.gov/ElectionOperations/DistrictLocator/AddressFinder.aspx Find your district/elected officials] \n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-break}}\n;Official campaign websites for 1st district candidates\n* [https://philaniseforcongress.com/ Philanise White (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 2nd district candidates\n* [http://www.robinkellyforcongress.org/ Robin Kelly (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.rabornforcongress.com/ Theresa Raborn (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 3rd district candidates\n* [https://mikefricilone.com/ Mike Fricilone (R) for Congress]\n* [https://www.marienewmanforcongress.com/ Marie Newman (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 4th district candidates\n* [http://jesuschuygarcia.com/ Jes\u00fas \"Chuy\" Garc\u00eda (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 5th district candidates\n* [https://quigleyforcongress.com/ Mike Quigley (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 6th district candidates\n* [https://castenforcongress.com/ Sean Casten (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.jeanneforcongress.com/ Jeanne Ives (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 7th district candidates\n* [https://www.dkdcongress.com/ Danny K. Davis (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 8th district candidates\n* [https://rajaforcongress.com/ Raja Krishnamoorthi (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 9th district candidates\n* [https://votesangari.com/ Sargis Sangari (R) for Congress]\n* [http://www.janschakowsky.org/ Jan Schakowsky (D) for Congress]\n{{col-break|gap=2em}}\n;Official c