o\n| length1 = 4:00\n\n| title2 = Tim McGraw\n| note2 = Live at Grand Ole Opry\n| length2 = 2:56\n\n| title3 = Tim McGraw\n| note3 = Live at [[Yahoo! Music]]\n| length3 = 4:05\n\n| title4 = Teardrops on My Guitar\n| note4 = music video\n| length4 = 3:45\n\n| title5 = Teardrops on My Guitar\n| note5 = behind the scenes\n| length5 = 4:16\n\n| title6 = Our Song\n| note6 = music video\n| length6 = 3:30\n\n| title7 = Our Song\n| note7 = behind the scenes\n| length7 = 11:30\n\n| title8 = A Place in This World\n| note8 = [[Great American Country|GAC]] ''Short Cut'' series\n| length8 = 21:48\n\n| title9 = Picture to Burn\n| note9 = CMT's unplugged at 330 sessions video performance\n| length9 = 3:14\n\n| title10 = Taylor's Home Movie\n| length10 = 5:40}}\n\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = [[Target Corporation|Target]] deluxe edition (bonus DVD)\n\n| title11 = Taylor's Performance on the [[Soul2Soul II Tour|Tim McGraw and Faith Hill Tour 2007]]\n| length11 = 10:12}}\n\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = Karaoke edition (CD/DVD)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Taylor-Swift/dp/B001NJY5Y4/|title=Taylor Swift: Taylor Swift|publisher=[[Amazon.com]] (US) Amazon.com Inc|accessdate=January 25, 2013}}</ref>\n\n| title1 = Tim McGraw\n| length1 = 3:52\n\n| title2 = Picture to Burn\n| length2 = 2:57\n\n| title3 = Teardrops on My Guitar\n| length3 = 3:24\n\n| title4 = A Place in This World\n| length4 = 3:22\n\n| title5 = Cold as You\n| length5 = 4:01\n\n| title6 = The Outside\n| length6 = 3:27\n\n| title7 = Tied Together with a Smile\n| length7 = 4:11\n\n| title8 = Stay Beautiful\n| length8 = 3:58\n\n| title9 = Should've Said No\n| length9 = 4:04\n\n| title10 = Mary's Song (Oh My My My)\n| length10 = 3:35\n\n| title11 = Our Song\n| length11 = 3:27\n\n| title12 = I'm Only Me When I'm with You\n| length12 = 3:33\n\n| title13 = Invisible\n| length13 = 3:24\n\n| title14 = Perfectly Good Heart\n| length14 = 3:42}}\n\n;Notes\n*<sup>{{note|a|[a]}}</sup> signifies an additional producer\n\n*\"I Heart ?\" was available as an exclusive download for copies of the album purchased at [[Best Buy]] during the first week of release.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Taylor-Swift-Taylor-Swift/release/12504513|title=Taylor Swift - Taylor Swift|website=Discogs|language=en|access-date=February 9, 2020}}</ref>\n*Initial pressings of the deluxe edition replaced the original versions of \"Teardrops on My Guitar\" and \"Our Song\" with their respective radio single versions. Later deluxe pressings also replaced \"Picture to Burn\" with its country radio edit and scrapped the bonus DVD and Swift's phone call with McGraw and replaced them with the pop version of \"Teardrops on My Guitar\".\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from the album's [[liner notes]]<ref name=\"liner\" />\n\n{{div col|colwidth=25em}}\n* [[Taylor Swift]] \u2013 lead vocals, background vocals, [[Songwriter|songwriting]], acoustic guitar\n* [[Nathan Chapman (record producer)|Nathan Chapman]] \u2013 acoustic guitar, banjo, bass, drums, electric guitar, engineer, background vocals, [[mandolin]], [[record producer|production]]\n* [[Scott Borchetta]] \u2013 [[executive producer]]\n* [[Chuck Ainlay]] \u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]]\n* Jeff Balding \u2013 mixing\n* [[Bruce Bouton]] \u2013 [[Dobro]]\n* Mike Brignardello \u2013 bass guitar\n* Nick Buda \u2013 drums\n* Gary Brunette \u2013 electric guitar\n* Jason Campbell \u2013 production coordination\n* Chason Carlson \u2013 [[audio engineer|engineer]]\n* Aaron Chmielewski \u2013 assistant engineer\n* [[Eric Darken]] \u2013 percussion\n* Allen Ditto \u2013 engineer\n* [[Dan Dugmore]] \u2013 [[pedal steel]]\n* [[Shannon Forrest]] \u2013 drums\n* Rob Hajacos \u2013 fiddle\n* Gordon Hammon \u2013 assistant engineer\n* Tony Harrell \u2013 keyboard\n* Jeffrey Hyde \u2013 banjo\n* Scott Kidd \u2013 mixing assistant\n* Greg Lawrence \u2013 mixing assistant\n* [[Andy Leftwich]] \u2013 fiddle, mandolin\n* Liana Ma